title: Brand New Round Rock Luxury Build! Pre-Leasing!
posting_body: ['This brand new build is currently pre-leasing for October!', "There's nothing like the comfort of knowing that you're among the first to live in your community.", 'Your unit will have airy, high ceilings, 8-foot high doors, granite countertops, washer and dryer in unit, and offers smart home technology packages.', 'The community offers tons green spaces, outdoor kitchens and an outdoor movie lawn, a resort style pool, and a fitness center with a yoga studio.', 'You will also have a professional grade tennis court and sand volley ball, and an activity lawn with games, and accessibility to walking trails.', 'Unit ID: 35912', 'Contact Randi at', 'show contact info', 'Licensed Agent', 'Apartment Specialists', 'Pricing and Availability Subject to Change']
